<SYNC START=1329852><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=1331497><P CLASS=KRCC>쏴라!
<SYNC START=1332954><P CLASS=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=1341035><P CLASS=KRCC>지옥으로 떨어져라
